Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:33.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Refrain　消した記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:39.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Rely　物語の常が今見せる言葉で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:41.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Don't end this, won't change it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}どうしたって　変えられない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:47.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}目的を忘れないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:55.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}誰が決めたんだ　そんな生き方らしくないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:02:01.26,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}やりたいこと貫く力　それこそが強さだって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:05.18,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}分かっているから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:07.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I believe in what I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}No reason to go back again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:14.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}歩んできた日々を　懐かしむ意味を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:16.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Easy losing memories
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:18.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I'm struggling now to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:23.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}諦めることはない　最後まで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Get down, let's get down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:32.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}心の光を　覚えてるうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:36.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Trust yourself. Don't be naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:41.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Save yourself. Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:33.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Refrain 抹去的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:39.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Rely 故事總在隻言片語間展開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:41.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Don't end this, won't change it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}無論怎麼做都無法改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:47.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}但不要忘記你的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:55.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}別人定義出的你 不是真實的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:02:01.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}堅持自我的力量 才是真的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:05.18,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}這就是我的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:07.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I believe in what I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}No reason to go back again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:14.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}我會回憶走過的路 找出價值所在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:16.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Easy losing memories
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:18.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I'm struggling now to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:23.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}我會堅持到最後 不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Get down, let's get down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:32.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}趁你心裡還亮著一團光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:36.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Trust yourself. Don't be naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:41.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Save yourself. Don't forget.
